Israel\" and \"airport on fire,\" what's your gut telling you? Is this a calculated military move, or are we watching two nations that genuinely believe the other one's existence is incompatible with their own? Because if Peggy's right, that changes *everything* about how we even talk about this. Stick with us\u2014we're digging deeper into what it means when nations stop negotiating and start reacting. Don't go anywhere.", "had_callers": false}, "timestamp": 1772970250229}
